        "culturalTip": "한국에서는 아플 때 '아이고'라고 말하기도 해요!",
        "explanationEn": "\"It is used when the body is not healthy or when there is pain.\"",
        "whenToUseEn": "\"When Describing Symptoms of Illness\"",
